Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, one day my passion's fire will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One day the flames would die out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought I didn't need anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But even now, I'm so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:02:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... but I'm gonna burn it up, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling, it's not that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely it's not that bad either
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
