Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,#10 The story of Tahomaru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There hasn't been any rain \Nfor 2 months now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If this drought continues, \Nit will affect the harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The neighboring Asakura clan \Nis getting restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotten news that they've been \Nquietly gathering an army at the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We should take action \Nbefore they start a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That grave face...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be related to the secret \NFather is keeping from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsu, Hyogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone from my family know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"HALL OF HELL"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be that baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still alive and is trying \Nto take his body back from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You done?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, that merchant says \Nthat the land is really rich there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The people eat all the white rice \Nthey want even in these times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go there next. We'll make \Nloads of money and stuff ourselves silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole sea breams, dried abalones, \Nmanju steamed buns...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Manju?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They're soft, sweet, and so delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll love them, just you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd been wanting to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a family seal on that amulet, right? \NIs it your family's?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've drugged him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll answer anything you ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My father has given you \Nspecial orders, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What were those orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To find a baby \Nthat disappeared 16 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and the midwife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is my father looking for a baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He tried to bite his tongue off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the cut is not deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The drug must've weakened him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, what is on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Asakura clan is getting restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, why are you searching for a baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A baby from over a decade ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That headless Goddess of Mercy \Nthat Mother worships,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,does it have anything to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please answer me, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It is none of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yet... \N-End of story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you still be alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you found me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You always came here as a child \Nwhenever anything happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And we came for you each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a child, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I must still seem like a child \Nto my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he won't take me to war \Nand keeps secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen my father \Nlooking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The matter with the baby  \N must mean that much to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, have mercy on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just leave us here to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me! Let go, or I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Tahomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We were passing through this village \Non our way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They suddenly stopped us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole village is going to be \Neaten up by the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A whirling current?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ripples in the water \Nsuddenly turn into a whirling current.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The current pulls you in, \Nand there's a huge mouth waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And it eats up our people, boat and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of our villagers \Nhave fallen victim to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A whirling current with a mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It does sound like the supernatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I will defeat it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Tahomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't believe these people, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it were true, \Nyou shouldn't be fighting monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,These people are not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My people are suffering. \NYou tell me to leave them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that is not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If the monster scares you, \Ngo ahead and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Tahomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:12:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to come, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be joking, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We would follow you \Neven into the depths of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The oar seems to be stuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! The monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to eat us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm, pull the ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You can't eat us \Njust by waiting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a crab! A monster crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What a hideous sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I will slay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's attacking from below.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Tahomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull the ropes, get back on land!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been hurt badly, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't come chasing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If it had stabbed a few more times, \Nthe boat would've sunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is disadvantageous for us \Nto fight on the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster eats with its mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We should carry explosives in our clothes \Nand make them explode as he swallows us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a hard shell, but a soft inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster will definitely be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So the one who is swallowed \Nwill die with the monster, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just said it'd kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We brothers only exist to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If we died, we couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So we will not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountains are green, \Nand the streams are flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The paddies are full of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Daigo's land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard it wasn't like this \Nbefore I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Floods kept the rice from growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,People chewed on tree roots  \N to keep from starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And who made this land so rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My father, Daigo Kagemitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am his son, Tahomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I will defeat any measly monster \Nwith my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What I need you to do is not to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just trust me. That's all I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo, lift me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher, even higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsu, gather everyone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our only way to defeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the sluice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many small lakes \Nalong the main lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We connected one with a sluice, \Nwith another sluice for draining.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you now. I will slay you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You all stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Mutsu, Hyogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-They're subduing that monster... \N-Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Tahomaru, \Nmake it pay for what it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Tahomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray for Sir Tahomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this, you monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me end your misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Guard the sluice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Young Master. \N-Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうふた月以上も雨が降っておりませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:13.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,れ以上続けば、収穫にも差し響きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:19.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿。隣国の朝倉に不審な動きが。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:26.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,にらみ合いが続く国境の町に密かに兵を\N集めているとの知らせが入っております。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:30.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,軍を興される前に、こちらから動くべきかと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:44.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのただならぬ様子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:51.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やはりあれこそ、父上たちが隠されていることでは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:53.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸奥。兵庫。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:57.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やってもらいたいことがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:00.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただし、家の者には知られるな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの赤子だな？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:37.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやつが生きて、貴様らに奪われた体を取り戻さんとしている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:39.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,答えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:13.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やはり…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:34.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,終わったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:35.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:42.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あちゃー…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:51.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でな。その商人のおっさんが言うには、\Nとにかく土地が豊かなんだって。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:56.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このご時世にみーんな白い飯を腹いっぱい食ってんだってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な？すごいだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:03.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,次はそこに決まりだな。がっぽり稼いでいいもんたらふく食うんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:07.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鯛のお頭焼きに、干しアワビにまんじゅうに…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:09.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,マンジュ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:15.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やわっこくて甘くて、とびっきり旨い食いモンだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:18.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まっ、楽しみにしときなって！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ…そういやぁ、前から気になってたんだけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:29.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのお守りの模様、そりゃ家紋だよな。兄貴の家のか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,薬を使いました。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:53.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どのようなことでも答えるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上から特別な命を申し付かっているな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:01.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何を命じられた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:07.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,16年前に消えた…赤子と…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,産婆を探せ…と…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:14.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,赤子だと？なぜ父親はその赤子を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,答えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:30.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,舌を噛み切ろうとしたようです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,助からぬか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:34.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いえ…傷は浅くにとどまっております
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,薬で力が入らなかったのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:58.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上。何をお考えですか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:02.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,朝倉が不穏な動きを見せておる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:04.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それだけですか。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:10.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上、なぜ赤子などお探しになられているのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:12.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それも10年以上も前の
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:17.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母が拝む首のない菩薩像。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:19.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれと関わりがあるのではありませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お答えください。父上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前は知らずともよい！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…ですが… \N二度は言わぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ生きていた…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よくここが分かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:15.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,幼少の頃は、何かあるとこの場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:18.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのたびにこうして迎えに来た。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:20.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつだって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:34.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,帰りましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,幼少の頃か…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:54.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上には、今も私が幼な子に見えるのだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:57.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だから戦にも出さぬし、隠し事もなさる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:02.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上のあのような顔、初めて見たわ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:08.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,赤子の件とは、それほどの大事か…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お願いしますだ、どうかご慈悲を
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:24.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おらたちを見捨てんでくだせぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:28.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えぇーい！貴様ら離さぬか！手をどけねば…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:29.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:32.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸様
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:36.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え…屋敷へ戻ろうとこの村を通りかかった折、
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:37.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この者たちが突然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:42.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうか…おらたちをお助けくだせぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:46.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ、村の者みんな化け物に食われちまいます！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:48.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,化け物だと！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,渦潮？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:06.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,湖面にさざ波が当たったと思ったら、突然渦潮に変わりやして…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:13.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それで、渦に引き寄せられてくと、\Nまるで人の口みたいなもんが待ち構えとるんです…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:16.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そいつが船ごと人を飲み込んです…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:21.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう何人も村のもんが犠牲になっております
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,渦潮に人の口か…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:28.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,確かに魑魅魍魎の類だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:32.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よかろう。私がその化け物を退治してくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸様。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:39.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この者たちの話を信じるおつもりですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:43.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よしんば真であったとしても、化け物退治など…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:46.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この者たちの言葉に嘘はない。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:49.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,民が苦しんでいるのに、放っておけと申すか！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,い、いえ、そのような…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:55.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,化け物に臆したのなら、お前たちだけ帰ればよい！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:56.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸様
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:12:00.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前たちも怖ければ来なくてよいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:02.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ご冗談でございましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:07.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うん！若が行くなら、地獄にだってついていく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:24.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それが…櫓が動かねんでさぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,来る！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:42.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でっ…出たぁ！バケモンだぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くっ…食われちまう！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:48.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うろたえるな！綱を引け！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:10.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうした。そこでじっとしていては、こちらを食うことはかなわんぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,か、カニだ！バケモンガニだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんと醜悪な姿よ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今すぐ叩き斬ってくれる！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:03.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,逃げた？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:09.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヤツめ！水中から！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:12.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸様！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,綱を引け！丘に上がる！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,相手も傷、軽くない…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:24.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だから追ってこれない…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:41.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あと数度突かれていたら、船が持ちませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:45.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やはり船上での戦いはこちらが不利かと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうする、若
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:57.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若。畏れながら…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやつも獲物を口で食らいまする。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:06.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あらかじめ懐に火薬を忍ばせ、飲まれた際炸裂させるのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,外は固くとも内は脆い。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:11.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,必ずや化け物を殺せましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:16.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,飲まれた者もろともな。化け物と心中か
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺たちがやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:21.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死ぬと言ったのだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死なない！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:28.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺たち兄弟は、若を守るためにいる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死んだら若を守れない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だから死なない！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:45.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見よ。この景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:49.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,山は緑が濃く\N泉は水に溢れ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,水田は稲で満ちている
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これが醍醐の土地だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:58.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが…私が生まれる前は違ったと聞く
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:02.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,水害によって稲は育たず
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:06.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,木の根を噛んで日々の飢えを凌ぐほどだったと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:09.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それをここまで立て直したのは誰か。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が父、醍醐景光だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:15.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私はその息子、多宝丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:19.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,化け物ごとき、この手で必ずや討ち果たしてみせよう！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:25.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前たちがすべきは、死ぬことではない。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:29.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私を信じる、ただそれだけで良い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:38.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫！私を担ぎ上げろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:40.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:46.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もっとだ！もっと高く！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:55.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸奥！皆を集めろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:04.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これしかヤツを討つ手立てはない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,容易いことではないが…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:09.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やってくれるな？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:42.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,現れたな、化け物め！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,水門を開け！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:58.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,湖の脇にはいくつもの小さな湖が点在しておる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:02.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その一つを水門で繋げ…別の水門から水を抜けば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このとおり…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:13.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姿を現しおったな！今度こそ斬ってくれる！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前たちは退がっていろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,来い、陸奥！兵庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:45.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんな恐ろしいバケモンを一方的に…\Nすげぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:51.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸様ー！おらたちのカタキを取ってくだせぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸様ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちくしょう、バケモンめ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:02.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,とっととくたばっちまえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これまでだな…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:10.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今楽にしてやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,水門を守れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:56.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待っていろ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:23.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:44.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前は…？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorrow scatters in the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.11,0:22:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,piling up to form shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Our footsteps admonish  \N indifference in such verbose ways
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:23:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As I peek into your fathomless eyes,  \N I lose my composure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any hope  \N in the place I am heading to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I feign amusement and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.39,0:23:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,because this road is so dark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be there to shine the light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to playing at saying goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I cried when I waved to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fiery woes fade... and fade...  \N until night falls upon us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew tomorrow would be so mundane,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have said that I wanted to live
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's futile but can't help dreaming  \N of a future... a future... you are to blame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bakemonogani"
